scenes.description: Watson Amelia introduces Koseki Bijou as the first guest for the Agent Test.
Watson Amelia introduces IRyS as the second guest.
Watson Amelia introduces Mori Calliope as the third guest.
Watson Amelia explains the rules of the 'Strength Test' to the participants.
Strength Test Level 1: Koseki Bijou attempts the Bazo weights lift.
Strength Test Level 1: IRyS attempts the Bazo weights lift.
